cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.CC, cs.AI, cs.DS

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with the logic induced by Computability Logic and its relationship with the cirquent calculus system CL15.
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses the parallel and branching recurrences in the context of computation.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is another possible category as the paper touches upon the complexity of the logic induced by Computability Logic.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a potential category as the paper may have implications for the development of AI systems that rely on logic.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the theoretical foundations of computation.
